
// The code constructs a greeting message using the [strings.builder] slot. It appends a salutation, a comma, a recipient's name, and an exclamation mark to form a complete string. The [strings.builder.append] slot is used multiple times to concatenate these elements sequentially.
strings.builder
   strings.builder.append:x:@.arguments/*/salutation
   strings.builder.append:", "
   strings.builder.append:x:@.arguments/*/recipient
   strings.builder.append:!
